---
description: DB access, transactions, and query safety
globs: "src/**/{repos,repositories,services,db}/**/*.ts"
alwaysApply: false
---

# DB conventions

- Never build queries via string concatenation; always use parameterized queries / safe ORM APIs.
- Use transactions for multi-step operations requiring atomicity.
- Repos do data access only; services own business rules and authorization decisions.
- Return domain-friendly results from repos (not Express responses).
